Put them on your IDL path, and edit accordingly bvls_external.pro to point to the right path. In your IDL routines replace bvls by bvls_external. That should do it.

Compilation instruction 
=======================

Linux/ifort

ifort -c bvls.f90
icc -c bvls_wrapper.c
ld -fPIC -shared -o bvls.so bvls.o bvls_wrapper.o

MAC:
gfortran -fexternal-blas -framework Accelerate  -march=native -dynamiclib -O3 -o bvls.dylib  bvls_wrapper.c bvls.f90 

